@startuml
title Leads - Blueprint Lifecycle (Zoho CRM UI DOM Scan)
[*] --> Not_Contacted : Lead Created (entry)
Not_Contacted --> Attempted         : [initial attempt made]
Not_Contacted --> Junk_Lead         : [marked junk]
Attempted --> Re_Attempted          : Re Attempted (transition button)
Attempted --> Contact_in_Future     : Contact in Future (transition button)
Attempted --> Lead                  : Lead (transition button)
Attempted --> Site_Visit_Completed  : Site Visit Completed (transition button)
Attempted --> Qualify_Out           : Qualify Out (transition button)
Attempted --> Junk_Lead             : Junk (transition button)
Attempted --> [*]                   : Exit Blueprint (transition button)
Contacted --> Book_Site_Visit       : Book Site Visit (transition button)
Contacted --> Attempted             : Attempted (transition button)
Contacted --> Contact_in_Future     : Contact in Future (transition button)
Contacted --> Site_Visit_Completed  : Site Visit Completed (transition button)
Contacted --> Qualify_Out           : Qualify Out (transition button)
Contacted --> Junk_Lead             : Junk (transition button)
Contacted --> [*]                   : Exit Blueprint (transition button)
Contact_in_Future --> Lead                  : Lead (transition button)
Contact_in_Future --> Attempted             : Attempted (transition button)
Contact_in_Future --> Site_Visit_Completed  : Site Visit Completed (transition button)
Contact_in_Future --> Junk_Lead             : Junk (transition button)
Contact_in_Future --> Deal_Closed           : Deal Closed (transition button)
Contact_in_Future --> [*]                   : Exit Blueprint (transition button)
Contact_in_Future --> Qualify_Out           : Qualify Out (transition button)
state "Lead Detail Actions" as LDA {
  LDA : Send Email
  LDA : Convert
  LDA : Edit
  LDA : Fetch Lead Status
